<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>ReneWangritte (Posts about Rene 愛亂吃)</title><link>http://renewang.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link type="application/rss+xml" href="http://renewang.github.io/categories/cat_rene-ai-luan-chi.xml" rel="self"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 26 Jul 2017 09:49:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>[Cook] 媽媽的廚房 - 從山上來的過貓</title><link>http://renewang.github.io/blog/2014/01/21/cook-ma-ma-de-chu-fang-cong-shan-shang-lai-de-guo-mao.html</link><dc:creator>Rene Wang</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tr-caption-container" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;text-align:center;"&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style="text-align:center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/renewangsl/11585144223/" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;" title="taiwanfood-06384.jpg by renewangsl, on Flickr"&gt;&lt;img alt="taiwanfood-06384.jpg" src="http://farm8.static.flickr.com/7366/11585144223_b9c52d1193_z.jpg" height="425" width="640"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td class="tr-caption" style="text-align:center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:small;"&gt;陪我們一起下山的過貓&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:purple;float:left;font-size:50px;line-height:55px;margin:5px 7px 0 0;"&gt;最&lt;/span&gt;近很流行一種取用在地食材和注重飲食健康的新北歐飲食 (New Nordic Cuisine)。新北歐飲食或又稱為斯堪地飲食，乍聽之下可能會與北歐簡約樸實的飲食風格發生聯想。甚至開始想像大塊麋鹿鹿排豪放隨意擺放在餐桌上，頂多加上一些新鮮莓果裝飾。而新北歐飲食的先鋒，來自丹麥的 Noma 餐廳主廚 Rene Redzepi 過去曾經在分子廚藝的 el Bulli 翹楚餐廳拜師學，則說：新北歐飲食的精神在於，好食物是可以發生在任何地方的！（good food can happen anywhere）&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://renewang.github.io/blog/2014/01/21/cook-ma-ma-de-chu-fang-cong-shan-shang-lai-de-guo-mao.html"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;由 Rene Redzepi 和多位北歐地區廚師起草的&lt;a href="http://newnordicfood.org/about-nnf-ii/new-nordic-kitchen-manifesto/" target="_blank"&gt;新北歐廚房規章…&lt;/a&gt; (1 min remaining to read)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>cook</category><category>Taiwan</category><guid>http://renewang.github.io/blog/2014/01/21/cook-ma-ma-de-chu-fang-cong-shan-shang-lai-de-guo-mao.html</guid><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2014 14:14:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>[Cook] 誰知盤中飧，粒粒皆辛苦</title><link>http://renewang.github.io/blog/2014/01/01/cook-shui-zhi-pan-zhong-sun-li-li-jie-xin-ku.html</link><dc:creator>Rene Wang</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;!–&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tr-caption-container" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;text-align:center;"&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style="text-align:center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/renewangsl/11584968095/" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;" title="taiwanfood-06454.jpg by renewangsl, on Flickr"&gt;&lt;img alt="taiwanfood-06454.jpg" src="http://farm8.static.flickr.com/7301/11584968095_ec77eeee17_z.jpg" height="425" width="640"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td class="tr-caption" style="text-align:center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:small;"&gt;頭低低的稻穗&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;–&amp;gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tr-caption-container" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;text-align:center;"&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style="text-align:center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/renewangsl/11584968095/" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;" title="taiwanfood-06454.jpg by renewangsl, on Flickr"&gt;&lt;img alt="taiwanfood-06454.jpg" src="http://farm8.static.flickr.com/7301/11584968095_ec77eeee17_b.jpg" height="425" width="640"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td class="tr-caption" style="text-align:center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:small;"&gt;頭低低的稻穗&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:purple;float:left;font-size:50px;line-height:55px;margin:5px 7px 0 0;"&gt;那&lt;/span&gt;時候，還是稻穗結實累累的秋天。每當微涼的秋風一吹動，負荷著結實稻米的稻穗就接二連三謙卑的彎下腰來，彷彿是一大片金黃色的海浪，邊前仆後繼的波動搖曳，邊隨著微風發出沙沙的聲音。我騎著腳踏車，路過這一片豐收的稻田，聽著“沙沙”的稻浪聲，猶如站在蔚藍的海岸邊，心裡是無比的恬靜和廣闊。&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://renewang.github.io/blog/2014/01/01/cook-shui-zhi-pan-zhong-sun-li-li-jie-xin-ku.html"&gt;Read more…&lt;/a&gt; (2 min remaining to read)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>cook</category><category>Taiwan</category><guid>http://renewang.github.io/blog/2014/01/01/cook-shui-zhi-pan-zhong-sun-li-li-jie-xin-ku.html</guid><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2014 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>[Tiramisu] 請帶我走...用提拉米蘇寫成的情書</title><link>http://renewang.github.io/blog/2013/06/06/tiramisu-qing-dai-wo-zou-yong-ti-la-mi-su-xie-cheng-de-qing-shu.html</link><dc:creator>Rene Wang</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tr-caption-container" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;text-align:center;"&gt;
